{
  "stem": "5188.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he inquired what different countries were offering, where there was free immigration, where there was a possibility of going.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he finally decided that we were going to go to Uruguay, in South America, to Montevideo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It seems that Uruguay had some kind of a law that-- like the American homestead law-- that if you wanted to be a farmer, they would give you land to cultivate.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you could immigrate into Uruguay without having anyone vouch for you or anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was an open country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my father says, that's the only way to get out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He'll get out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Incidentally, he didn't want to go to Europe anywhere, because he felt that he had to get away from Europe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He-- he was afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this was-- and I don't know why he felt that, but he was not about to go to France or to England or anywhere like that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He wanted to get far away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we couldn't go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he was going to go to Uruguay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they switched at the Berlitz school from English lessons to Spanish lessons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember that very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I didn't get any lessons, because they felt, well, I'm too young.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I'm not going to-- I'll learn whenever I get there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was the attitude.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So-- but my sister was studying, because they felt that she probably would have to go to work or something, and she needed to know the language of wherever we were going.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we had all kinds of material in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I remember reading the-- the-- the folders, and looking at the pictures of going to South America.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were all set.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
